These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, december, june
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris, dahlia, daisy
1. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the indonesian is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking sprite##2
3. the colombian is the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee | sprite   | milk  | hot-chocolate  |
| Birthday   | january    | june    | july      | december    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Flower     | daisy  | aconite       | iris    | dahlia     |

