.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, canadian, turkish, dutch
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, grey, pink, amber
There 4 different types of food: cherry, kiwi, orange, lime
1. the person eating lime is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the french is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes amber is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the turkish is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person who likes pink and the person eating cherry##2
6. the person eating lime is between the person watching western movies and the person who likes amber##2
7. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the turkish##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality         | dutch | canadian    | turkish  | french    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Color           | amber      | pink       | grey      | white       |
| Food         | kiwi    | lime | orange | cherry |

