.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, soccer, rowing, weightlifting
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, coffee, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, satire, horror, family
1. the paramedic is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the lawyer is the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking almond-milk##2
9. the person drinking coffee is between the person who's sport is rowing and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Sport        | soccer | rowing     | cricket   | weightlifting     |
| Beverage       | 7up   | juice   | coffee | almond-milk |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | satire | thriller  | family    |

