.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, dancing, reading
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, daffodil, rose
City: new-york, venice, hannover, nizza
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is the fisherman##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who growsorchid##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the police-officer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
10. the mechanic is between the person who growsdahlia and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Hobby   | reading | hiking  | dancing | rock-climbing       |
| Flower           | orchid       | rose    | daffodil      | dahlia           |
| City         | new-york | venice   | nizza   | hannover         |

