.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, go, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, milk, hot-chocolate
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, palace, art-deco
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing go is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person playing go is on the left of the palace house##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person playing billiard is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the art-deco house and the person drinking cola##2
10. the person drinking milk is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Game           | go | scrabble | monopoly    | billiard     |
| Beverage   | cola      | milk       | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk       |
| House         | gothic-revival     | palace       | art-deco | craftsman |

