.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, librarian, paramedic
City: venice, london, colone, paris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, fantasy, scientific, time-travel
4 different games are played: poker, chess, scrabble, canasta
1. the person traveling to venice is between the person playing canasta and the person traveling to colone##2
2. the freelancer is between the person traveling to venice and the person watching time-travel movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is between the person playing chess and the person watching fantasy movies##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| City   | london      | paris       | venice     | colone      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | fantasy      | scientific   | musical   |
| Game         | scrabble   | canasta    | poker | chess   |

