.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold, lily, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, juice, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, goldfish, cat
 1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is the dutch##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is between the dutch and the owner of the goldfish##2
 4. the person drinking juice is the owner of the cat##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the argentine is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growslily##1
10. the dutch is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | lily | marigold | sunflower  | poppy  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea       | juice   | coffee | tea    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| Pet     | mouse    | cat   | guinea-pig    | goldfish  |

