3. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating plum##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
