.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, spinach, tomato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, drama, superhero
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, collecting, traveling
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, cat, mouse
 1. the person eating lettuce is the person watching drama movies##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is the owner of the horse##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the owner of the goldfish##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Movie-Genre           | superhero | thriller | mystery   | drama |
| Hobby   | collecting         | hiking       | traveling      | card-games     |
| Pet         | cat       | mouse | goldfish    | horse  |

