4 different games are played: whist, chess, scrabble, poker
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person playing poker is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to venice##2
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person playing chess##1
10. the person who growspoppy is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to venice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
