The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, sailing, tennis
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, satire, musical, comedy
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the photographer##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing bridge and the person playing canasta##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the freelancer##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing canasta is the person watching musical movies##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
