4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person who likes green is the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the musician is on the right of the person who likes green##1
8. the designer is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
9. the electrician is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color        | blue     | emerald  | green     | orange     |
| Flower       | marigold   | tulip  | azalea   | sunflower   |
| Job         | writer    | designer | electrician | musician |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up     | coffee      | sprite      |

