 3. the indonesian is between the person driving the van and the person driving the motorbike##2
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the person who likes black is the indonesian##1
10. the person who likes azure is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4     |
| Color      | orange     | azure         | black   | grey |
| Transport          | subway | motorbike    | scooter   | van   |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | ambient | d&b   | rock   |
| Nationality   | argentine | japanese     | indonesian | american |

 